data.description: PRICE REDUCED* STUNNING home located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Fox Hollow. This inviting 3 bed, 2 bath home features an open layout with REAL wood floors and large guest bedrooms. The kitchen is equipped with a butcher clock island, tall upper cabinets, and a large deep sink. The living area features custom crown molding and a cozy wood-burning fireplace. Primary suite boasts a California Closets walk-in custom closet, garden tub, and double sinks. The home has unique architectural touches with rounded corners and arches. Enjoy a cup of coffee on the covered front porch. Fence was replaced in 2021 and both HVAC units replaced in December of 2020. See complete list of updates in supplements. Located in Red Oak ISD with easy access to I-35. Your dream home awaits! This ONE IS A STEAL!
